{"tid":18644,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[壁球女團世錦賽] 4強 香港 VS 英格蘭 12am直播","createTime":"2016-12-02T11:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T06:55:10.000Z","uid":18692,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6748baf68092a731404b61ba32b74e19a634b8e0","tid":18644,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T11:46:58.000Z","msg":"女子世界團體錦標賽2016八強賽事展開，第四種籽的香港隊，成員包括歐詠芝，陳浩鈴，廖梓苓及湯芷穎以2-1擊退三號種籽兼上屆亞軍馬來西亞，連續兩屆成功打入四強。<br />\n<br />\n陳浩鈴打頭陣與地利亞萊奮戰五局後以8-11，11-5，9-11，11-3及11-6取得開局勝利，為香港帶來領先優勢。<br />\n<br />\n歐詠芝雖以直落三局不敵前世界一姐妮高，但湯芷穎於決勝局中表現出色，雖曾於第二局長刁時落敗，仍能沉著應戰終以11-9，15-17，13-11及11-6淘汰斯華，香港再度晉級準決賽。<br />\n<br />\n香港將與二號種籽及衛冕冠軍英格蘭，香港時間星期六凌晨十二時爭入決賽。"},{"pid":"a5b963b4b6ad59ce84320431d8258fd01c24c13e","tid":18644,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T11:48:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=EtP-cYTimJ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fwatch%3Ffeature%3Dyoutu.be%26v%3DEtP-cYTimJ4&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iStwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=72cd6712\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=EtP-cYTimJ4</a><br />\n官方直播link <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b7410b3b1a48dfb6a771f8fed38305323c9e24","tid":18644,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T11:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6272cfde5e93582615bf47dd3198762bcea6dd58","tid":18644,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T12:09:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://68.media.tumblr.com/f52019029743d5c3d783b2f1087dba9a/tumblr_inline_ohjr84lfu01s38j9i_1280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2Ff52019029743d5c3d783b2f1087dba9a%2Ftumblr_inline_ohjr84lfu01s38j9i_1280.png&h=b62a1994&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcfc6de345ffcdd585d95461e96a93a1